Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:23.27,Romaji ED 2,ShinkaDan,0,0,0,,Разбуди непобедимое сердце!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:27.20,Romaji ED 4,ShinkaDan,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Osoreru koto nai revives my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:27.20,Romaji ED 2,ShinkaDan,0,0,0,,Нечего бояться, возроди свое сердце!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:36.09,Romaji ED 4,ShinkaDan,0,0,0,,{\fs34\blur5\fad(0,450)}Namida o nagashita ato ni wa mutekina watashi to ashita ni cheers!
